            <title>[FELIX-1926] Access to internal maps in the ComponentRegistry must be guarded against concurrency issues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1926</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently accesses to the internal m_componetsById and m_compeontsByName maps are not guarded against concurrent calls and thus become corrupt in highly concurrent situations.&lt;/p&gt;

